KnockOut.name: Knock Out
KnockOut.plot: After the sudden death of his father and the weight of inherited debts, Keen seeks refuge at a Muay Thai camp where he meets Than, an elite but reluctant fighter; through training, competition, and shared struggles in and out of the ring, relationships deepen and challenges mount against the backdrop of Muay Thai culture and personal resilience. :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}
